00:15:37.996 --> 00:15:42.820 align:middle line:90%


00:15:42.820 --> 00:15:45.160 align:middle line:84%
>> The transformative,
and even magical,

00:15:45.160 --> 00:15:49.210 align:middle line:84%
powers of words is recognized
in spiritual traditions all over

00:15:49.210 --> 00:15:51.010 align:middle line:90%
the world.

00:15:51.010 --> 00:15:54.490 align:middle line:10%
The word "spell" comes from
Proto-German "spellen,"

00:15:54.490 --> 00:15:56.110 align:middle line:10%
meaning "to tell."

00:15:56.110 --> 00:15:58.660 align:middle line:84%
And the word "abracadabra"
was originally

00:15:58.660 --> 00:16:01.570 align:middle line:84%
a Hebrew word which
Kabbalistic practitioners

00:16:01.570 --> 00:16:06.530 align:middle line:84%
use to mean, "I create
according to my word."

00:16:06.530 --> 00:16:09.380 align:middle line:84%
Mantras are among the
most ancient of these word

00:16:09.380 --> 00:16:12.560 align:middle line:84%
formulations and can also be
used for magical purposes.

00:16:12.560 --> 00:16:15.300 align:middle line:90%


00:16:15.300 --> 00:16:17.900 align:middle line:84%
>> Mantras can be
tools for meditation,

00:16:17.900 --> 00:16:19.280 align:middle line:90%
for calming the mind.

00:16:19.280 --> 00:16:21.500 align:middle line:84%
And then they can
be, essentially,

00:16:21.500 --> 00:16:24.440 align:middle line:84%
the equivalent of
magical spells that are

00:16:24.440 --> 00:16:27.140 align:middle line:90%
accomplishing specific tasks.

00:16:27.140 --> 00:16:32.480 align:middle line:84%
Where you receive a mantra
from a guru or master who

00:16:32.480 --> 00:16:36.020 align:middle line:84%
has infused it with some of the
energy of their own awakening,

00:16:36.020 --> 00:16:38.540 align:middle line:84%
and they received it from
their teacher who infused it

00:16:38.540 --> 00:16:41.000 align:middle line:84%
with some of the energy
of their awakening,

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:44.510 align:middle line:84%
those are considered the
most powerful mantras

00:16:44.510 --> 00:16:46.430 align:middle line:84%
because those
mantras help activate

00:16:46.430 --> 00:16:51.320 align:middle line:84%
the energy of waking
up in your system

00:16:51.320 --> 00:16:56.240 align:middle line:84%
at a kind of transmental
level, at a level beyond what

00:16:56.240 --> 00:16:59.000 align:middle line:84%
the rational mind
can comprehend.

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:02.870 align:middle line:84%
Because mantras partake
of awakened consciousness,

00:17:02.870 --> 00:17:04.520 align:middle line:84%
the degree of your
own awakeness will

00:17:04.520 --> 00:17:10.970 align:middle line:84%
determine the power with which
the mantra is able to operate.

00:17:10.970 --> 00:17:13.490 align:middle line:84%
>> The text I worked on for
my PhD has a what's called

00:17:13.490 --> 00:17:14.510 align:middle line:90%
a mantra dhara.

00:17:14.510 --> 00:17:18.380 align:middle line:84%
So that's like a sort of
cryptic riddle or puzzle

00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:20.439 align:middle line:84%
from which you
extract the mantra.

00:17:20.439 --> 00:17:23.930 align:middle line:84%
And If you repeat that mantra
hundreds of thousands of times,

00:17:23.930 --> 00:17:27.980 align:middle line:84%
then you will achieve various
magical powers and so forth.

00:17:27.980 --> 00:17:31.880 align:middle line:84%
But also your mind will expand
and become one with the ether.

00:17:31.880 --> 00:17:37.760 align:middle line:84%
So that's kind of seen as being
equivalent to enlightenment.

00:17:37.760 --> 00:17:41.600 align:middle line:84%
There are lots, and lots, and
lots of texts teaching mantras

00:17:41.600 --> 00:17:44.800 align:middle line:84%
which can be used for kind of
black magic, supernatural ends,

00:17:44.800 --> 00:17:48.650 align:middle line:84%
how to repeat this mantra
100,000 times whilst offering

00:17:48.650 --> 00:17:51.320 align:middle line:84%
this into the fire, and, yeah,
your neighbor's goat will

00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:52.183 align:middle line:90%
fall over.

00:17:52.183 --> 00:17:54.320 align:middle line:84%
Or something like
that, you know?

00:17:54.320 --> 00:17:55.780 align:middle line:90%
Sometimes it's as basic as that.

00:17:55.780 --> 00:17:58.940 align:middle line:84%
It's kind of
mumbo-jumbo black magic.

00:17:58.940 --> 00:18:01.810 align:middle line:84%
>> The ultimate goal of that
mantra is self-realization.

00:18:01.810 --> 00:18:03.710 align:middle line:84%
But to get there,
this may come to you.

00:18:03.710 --> 00:18:04.970 align:middle line:90%
You become very concentrated.

00:18:04.970 --> 00:18:06.500 align:middle line:90%
People start liking you.

00:18:06.500 --> 00:18:07.760 align:middle line:90%
Maybe money will come to you.

00:18:07.760 --> 00:18:08.677 align:middle line:90%
You become successful.

00:18:08.677 --> 00:18:10.360 align:middle line:84%
Different types of
things will happen

00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:12.590 align:middle line:84%
as you go through
different stages,

00:18:12.590 --> 00:18:15.530 align:middle line:84%
through different chakras,
through different chis,

00:18:15.530 --> 00:18:17.850 align:middle line:84%
different levels
of concentration.

00:18:17.850 --> 00:18:20.370 align:middle line:84%
Every day, you wake
up to a new world,

00:18:20.370 --> 00:18:25.024 align:middle line:90%
new experiences, new abilities.

00:18:25.024 --> 00:18:27.469 align:middle line:90%
[CHANTING]

00:18:27.469 --> 00:18:32.860 align:middle line:90%


00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:36.310 align:middle line:84%
>> While most scholars agree
the development of lower siddhis

00:18:36.310 --> 00:18:40.240 align:middle line:84%
or psychic powers is largely
a waste of precious time

00:18:40.240 --> 00:18:44.890 align:middle line:84%
and effort, the allure of the
siddhis has led to many means

00:18:44.890 --> 00:18:46.720 align:middle line:90%
of trickery.

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:49.383 align:middle line:84%
>> The idea of the siddhis--
and they're powerful things--

00:18:49.383 --> 00:18:50.800 align:middle line:84%
show there's a
very long tradition

00:18:50.800 --> 00:18:54.550 align:middle line:84%
in every culture of people who
fake these things because they

00:18:54.550 --> 00:18:56.600 align:middle line:90%
know it will delight people.

00:18:56.600 --> 00:19:00.070 align:middle line:84%
And there's also a
whole thread of people

00:19:00.070 --> 00:19:02.920 align:middle line:84%
who fake these
kinds of powers, who

00:19:02.920 --> 00:19:04.840 align:middle line:84%
make it a very
blurry distinction

00:19:04.840 --> 00:19:07.220 align:middle line:84%
as to whether they're
real or not real.

00:19:07.220 --> 00:19:09.937 align:middle line:84%
So if you go to a magician
who does illusions onstage,

00:19:09.937 --> 00:19:11.020 align:middle line:90%
you know that that's fake.

00:19:11.020 --> 00:19:12.520 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't matter
how good it looks.

00:19:12.520 --> 00:19:13.345 align:middle line:90%
You know it's fake.

00:19:13.345 --> 00:19:15.950 align:middle line:84%
But if you see somebody
on the street doing it,

00:19:15.950 --> 00:19:17.740 align:middle line:84%
and they don't look
like a magician,

00:19:17.740 --> 00:19:19.615 align:middle line:84%
and they don't sound
like it, and everything,

00:19:19.615 --> 00:19:21.100 align:middle line:90%
it's very hard to tell.

00:19:21.100 --> 00:19:24.040 align:middle line:84%
However, in the "Yoga Sutras"
and in other traditions,

00:19:24.040 --> 00:19:26.470 align:middle line:84%
there is a very
strict prohibition

00:19:26.470 --> 00:19:28.710 align:middle line:84%
about demonstrating the
powers that you gain.

00:19:28.710 --> 00:19:31.220 align:middle line:84%
So if you gain real
powers of these types,

00:19:31.220 --> 00:19:34.600 align:middle line:84%
whether it's simple
telepathy or levitation,

00:19:34.600 --> 00:19:36.880 align:middle line:84%
there it specifically said
in one of the "Sutras,"

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:39.010 align:middle line:90%
do not demonstrate this--

00:19:39.010 --> 00:19:40.250 align:middle line:90%
and for good reason.

00:19:40.250 --> 00:19:42.910 align:middle line:84%
The reason is that
power is seductive.

00:19:42.910 --> 00:19:44.980 align:middle line:84%
And the yogis knew
this long ago.

00:19:44.980 --> 00:19:47.650 align:middle line:84%
You gain a certain power,
and you're excited about it.

00:19:47.650 --> 00:19:49.400 align:middle line:84%
You want to demonstrate
it to people.

00:19:49.400 --> 00:19:50.680 align:middle line:84%
So there's two reasons
not to do that.

00:19:50.680 --> 00:19:52.888 align:middle line:84%
First of all, other people
will begin to worship you,

00:19:52.888 --> 00:19:54.910 align:middle line:84%
and your ego will
become inflamed,

00:19:54.910 --> 00:19:56.800 align:middle line:90%
and then you become Darth Vader.

00:19:56.800 --> 00:19:58.750 align:middle line:84%
And the other is
that it deflects

00:19:58.750 --> 00:20:02.050 align:middle line:84%
from the original purpose of
yoga, which is not the powers.

00:20:02.050 --> 00:20:03.790 align:middle line:90%
It was enlightenment.

00:20:03.790 --> 00:20:05.730 align:middle line:84%
So the very people,
as a scientist,

00:20:05.730 --> 00:20:08.540 align:middle line:84%
who I want to study
in the laboratory,

00:20:08.540 --> 00:20:10.490 align:middle line:90%
they follow the prohibitions.

00:20:10.490 --> 00:20:12.730 align:middle line:84%
So only on a few
occasions have I

00:20:12.730 --> 00:20:15.940 align:middle line:84%
worked with people who have
long traditions in the siddhis,

00:20:15.940 --> 00:20:19.150 align:middle line:84%
and can probably do them,
who worked with experiments

00:20:19.150 --> 00:20:22.510 align:middle line:84%
under controlled conditions
and did extremely well.

00:20:22.510 --> 00:20:24.900 align:middle line:84%
So in one case, I saw a
really, really good result

00:20:24.900 --> 00:20:25.700 align:middle line:90%
in the laboratory.

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:28.270 align:middle line:84%
And I knew this guy came
from a Himalayan tradition

00:20:28.270 --> 00:20:30.280 align:middle line:84%
where they study
the siddhis, and he

00:20:30.280 --> 00:20:32.213 align:middle line:90%
had been doing it for 70 years.

00:20:32.213 --> 00:20:34.630 align:middle line:84%
This was an experiment looking
at this quantum measurement

00:20:34.630 --> 00:20:36.700 align:middle line:84%
problem with the
movement of light.

00:20:36.700 --> 00:20:39.610 align:middle line:84%
So he was able to change
the behavior of light, which

00:20:39.610 --> 00:20:42.040 align:middle line:84%
was in a shielded room next
door, simply by sitting

00:20:42.040 --> 00:20:43.150 align:middle line:90%
there and meditating.

00:20:43.150 --> 00:20:46.270 align:middle line:84%
So I asked him, how
did you do that?

00:20:46.270 --> 00:20:49.150 align:middle line:84%
How did you make this
system change at a distance?

00:20:49.150 --> 00:20:52.630 align:middle line:84%
And all he would do was
smile because you're not

00:20:52.630 --> 00:20:54.790 align:middle line:84%
supposed to demonstrate
it, which he kind of did

00:20:54.790 --> 00:20:56.150 align:middle line:90%
in a controlled environment.

00:20:56.150 --> 00:20:58.520 align:middle line:84%
But he certainly wasn't going
to tell me how he did it.

00:20:58.520 --> 00:20:59.320 align:middle line:90%
